title: DDFP 228: Super Bowl XLVIII Special, Day 2
itunes:title: DDFP 228: Super Bowl XLVIII Special, Day 2
description:
Shek, Rank, Matt "Money" Smith and Molly Qerim check in from the Super Bowl XLVIII festivities in New York, this time alongside another catalog of stars from the world of sports and entertainment.  Don’t miss interviews with Kid Cudi, Aaron Paul, Jamaal Charles, Jerry Rice and many more on this jam-packed episode of The Dave Dameshek Football Program.  For more, be sure to follow @NFLcomLIVE -- the official handle for "NFL.com Live: Super Bowl XLVIII."
